a artiglieria.png|30px]] \"'Artillery School\"', in [[Bracciano]]\n*** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 001.png|25px]] 1st Artillery (Training) Group \"[[Hunters of the Alps|Cacciatore delle Alp]]i\", in Bracciano \n**** 1st battery with M114 155mm towed howitzers\n**** 2nd battery with FH-70 155mm towed howitzers\n**** 3rd battery with M109 self-propelled howitzers\n**** 4th battery with [[Palmaria (artillery)|SP-70]] self-propelled howitzers and [[MRLS]] (disbanded during 1989)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA scuola genio.png|30px]] \"'Engineer School\"', in Rome\n*** 4th Engineer (Recruits Training) Battalion \"M.O. Montorsi\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 08.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Lancieri di Montebello\" (8th)|8th Mechanized Squadrons Group \"Lancieri di Montebello\"]], in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 028.png|25px]] 28th Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"[[Pavia]]\", in [[Pesaro]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 080.png|25px]] 80th Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"Roma\", in [[Cassino]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 084.png|25px]] 84th Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"[[Venice|Venezia]]\", in [[Falconara Marittima]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 123.png|25px]] 123rd Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"Chieti\", in [[Chieti]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt genio 06.png|25px]] 6th Engineer Battalion \"[[Lake Trasimeno|Trasimeno]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasmissioni 44.png|25px]] 44th Signal Battalion \"[[Penne, Abruzzo|Penne]]\", in Rome\n*** 26th Signal Company, in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasporti 08.png|25px]] 8th Mixed Transport Battalion \"[[Via Casilina|Casilina]]\", in Rome\n** 28th Army Light Aviation Squadrons Group \"[[Tucana|Tucano]]\", at [[Rome Viterbo Airport|Rome-Viterbo Air Base]], ([[SIAI-Marchetti SM.1019|SM-1019]] planes and [[Bell 206|AB-206]] helicopters)\n** '''\"Lazio\" Mechanized Brigade''' (Wartime mobilization)\n*** Command and Signal Unit (to be formed