ico granatieri.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Civitavecchia\n** Anti-tank Company \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Civitavecchia\n** Engineer Company \"Granatieri di Sardegna\", in Civitavecchia\n\n==== Motorized Brigade \"Acqui\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA mot bde Acqui.png|30px]] '''[[Acqui Motorized Brigade|Motorized Brigade \"Acqui\"]]''', in [[L'Aquila]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Acqui Terme|Acqui]]\", in L'Aquila\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg corazzato 09.png|25px]] 9th Armored Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Butera\", in L'Aquila, (two [[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] tanks companies and one [[M113 armored personnel carrier|M113]] mech infantry company)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 017.png|25px]] 17th Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"[[Battle of Solferino|San Martino]]\", in [[Sulmona]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 057.png|25px]] 57th Motorized Infantry Battalion \"[[Abruzzo|Abruzzi]]\", in [[Sora, Lazio|Sora]]\n** 70th Motorized (Reserve) Infantry Battalion \"Ancona\", in Sulmona\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 130.png|25px]] 130th Motorized Infantry Battalion \"[[Perugia]]\", in [[Spoleto]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 048.png|25px]] 48th Field Artillery Group \"[[Taro (river)|Taro]]\", in L'Aquila, ([[M114 155 mm howitzer|M114 155mm]] towed [[howitzer]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico acqui.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Acqui\", in L'Aquila\n** Anti-tank Company \"Acqui\", in L'Aquila\n** Engineer Company \"Acqui\", in L'Aquila\n\n=== Southern Military Region ===\n* '''Southern Military Region''' (R.M.M.), in [[Naples]], responsible for the regions of [[Apulia]], [[Basilicata]], [[Campania]] and [[Calabria]]\n** R.M.M. Command Unit, in Naples\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA scuola cavalleria.png|30px]] '''Armored Troops School''', in [[Lecce]]\n*** Command Unit, in Lecce\n*** 21st Tank (Recruits Training) Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Scognamiglio\" (Reserve),