iete - 50 btg log di manovra Carnia.png|25px]] 50th Maneuver Logistic Battalion \"[[Carnia]]\", in Pordenone\n\n==== Armored Brigade \"Mameli\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA arm bde Mameli.png|30px]] '''[[Mameli Armored Brigade|Armored Brigade \"Mameli\"]]''', in [[Spilimbergo|Tauriano]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Goffredo Mameli|Mameli]]\", in Tauriano\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 19.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Cavalleggeri Guide\" (19th)|19th Reconnaissance Squadrons Group \"Cavalleggeri Guide\"]], in [[Casarsa della Delizia]] (two Leopard 1A2 tank companies and one VCC-2 mech infantry company)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 032.png|25px]] 3rd Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Galas\", in Tauriano, ([[M60 Patton|M60A1]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg carri 005.png|25px]] 5th Tank Battalion \"M.O. Chiamenti\", in Tauriano, (M60A1 main battle tanks)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt bersaglieri 12.png|25px]] 23rd [[Bersaglieri]] Battalion \"Castel di Borgo\", in Tauriano, ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-1]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA grp artiglieria 012.png|25px]] 12th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"[[Capua]]\", in [[Spilimbergo|Vacile]], ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-propelled howitzers]])\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico mameli.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Mameli\", in Vacile\n** Anti-tank Company \"Mameli\", in Vacile\n** Engineer Company \"Mameli\", in Vacile\n\n==== Armored Brigade \"Ariete\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA arm bde ariete.png|30px]] '''[[Ariete Armored Brigade|Armored Brigade \"Ariete\"]]''', in [[Pordenone]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"Ariete\", in [[Pordenone]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 132.png|25px]] 8th Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Secchiaroli\", in Aviano, ([[M60 Patton|M60A1]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 133.png|25px]] 10th Tank Battalion \"M.O. Bruno\", in Aviano, (M60A1 main battle tanks)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg corazzato 13.png|25px]] 13th Tank Battalion \"M.O. Pascucci\", in [[Cordenons]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] main battle tanks) (Reserve status from December 1989, reassigned to \"Mantova\" Brigade)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg bersaglieri 28.png|25px]] 27th Bersaglieri Battalion \"[[Battle of Doberd\u00f2|Jamiano]]\", in Aviano, ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-1]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA grp artiglieria 020.png|25px]] 20th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"[[Battle of the Piave River|Piave]]\", in [[Maniago]], ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-propelled howitzers]])\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico ariete.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Ariete\", in Maniago\n** Anti-tank Company \"Ariete\", in Aviano\n** Engineer Company \"Ariete\", in Maniago\n\n==== Armored Brigade \"Pozzuolo del Friuli\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA cav bde Pozzuolo del Friuli.png|30px]] '''[[Pozzuolo del Friuli Cavalry Brigade|Armored Brigade \"Pozzuolo del Friuli\"]]''', in [[Palmanova]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Pozzuolo del Friuli]]\" , in Palmanova\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 04.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Genova Cavalleria\" (4th)|4th Mechanized Squadrons Group \"Genova Cavalleria\"]], in Palmanova, ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 05.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Lancieri di Novara\" (5th)|5th Tank Squadrons Group \"Lancieri di Novara\"]], in [[Codroipo]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 28.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Cavalleggeri di Treviso\" (28th)|28th Tank Squadrons Group \"Cavalleggeri di Treviso\"]], in Palmanova, (Leopard 1A2 main battle tanks)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA grp artiglieria 120.png|25px]] 120th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"Po\", in Palmanova, ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-