p \"[[Dragon|Drago]]\", in [[Alghero-Fertilia Airport|Alghero-Fertilia]], detached to the military intelligence agency [[SISMI]]\n*** 51st Medium Helicopter Squadrons Group \"[[Leo (constellation)|Leone]]\", in Viterbo, ([[Bell 412|AB-412]] [[utility helicopter]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg NBC 01.png|25px]] 1st [[CBRN defense|CBRN-defense]] Battalion \"[[Etruria]]\", in [[Rieti]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg ricel 08.png|25px]] 8th [[ELINT]] Battalion \"[[Tonale Pass|Tonale]]\", in [[Anzio]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg guelt 09.png|25px]] 9th [[Electronic Warfare]] Battalion \"[[Timmelsjoch|Rombo]]\", in Anzio\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasmissioni 03.png|25px]] 10th Signal Battalion \"[[Lanciano]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasmissioni 11.png|25px]] 11th Signal Battalion \"[[Leonessa]]\", in Civitavecchia\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA autogr manovra 10.png|25px]] 10th Joint Transport Battalion \"[[Via Salaria|Salaria]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA autogr manovra 11.png|25px]] 11th Transport Battalion \"[[Via Flaminia|Flaminia]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 1.png|25px]] 1st Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Hydra (constellation)|Idra]]\", in [[Bracciano]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 2.png|25px]] 2nd Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Orion (constellation)|Orione]]\", in [[Bologna]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 3.png|25px]] 3rd Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Aquila (constellation)|Aquila]]\", in [[Orio al Serio]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 4.png|25px]] 4th Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Scorpius|Scorpione]]\", in [[Viterbo]]\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Structure of the Italian Army]] for the current structure of the [[Italian Army]].\n\n[[Category:Structure of contemporary armies|Italian Army]]\n[[Category:Army units and formations of Italy]]\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n[[Category:Structures of military commands and formations in 1989]]\n[[Category:Italian Army (post-1946)]]\n", "